abstract: Day 2 of our week-long puzzle contest.
snippet: Day 2 of our week-long puzzle contest.
lead_paragraph: Administrivial Tournament Reminder! It's not too late to sign up for the Westchester Crossword Puzzle Tournament, held this year on Friday, October 21 at Will Shortz's Westchester Table Tennis Club. New York Times crossword puzzles, mouth-watering desserts, and additional puzzles by our puzzle master make for an evening of fun that raises money for a great cause, the Pleasantville Fund For Learning. You can even pay at the door, so if you will be in the area, stop by and say hello. I'll be there to greet you, but I'm just warning you: the brownies are mine. All mine.

headline.main: Tuesday: Day Two of the Crossword Contest
